dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Atlantic City, New Jersey : including Ventnor, South Atlantic City & Longport (Special Index)
dct_description_sm: Includes key, streets and specials index, and text. "9082." North oriented towards upper right. Sheets 67-68 show Ventnor; sheet 69 shows Atlantic City; sheet 70 shows Longport.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn Map Company, 1906, c1907.
